EG, VG, Secret, C9. Long ago, the four teams played together in harmony. Then, everything changed when the Great Immigration happened. Only Arteezy, master of all four roles, could stop them, but when EG needed him most, he vanished. A hundred years passed and my brother and I discovered the new Arteezy, a potato farmer named Artour. And although his midas skills are great, he has a lot to learn before he's ready to win anything.

I personally love lumi's casting...I learn so much. Whenever he makes a statement I know that the opposite of his statement is true. This has allowed me to gain an un-matchable understanding of dota and has helped to reach 9k mmr.
